<br>
The big trick to getting the SoM is safely negotiating the Protectors of Zek.  Once you figure out how to safely split them you could concivibly use one group of 55+ to take them  down and pull B-man the Cold.  The scepter isn't his common drop, so be prepared to sit there a while and up your dragon faction a bit. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->      <br>
<br>
I'll try to explain and show how I split the PoZ's...this is just my method.  I'm sure there are much better!<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://communities.msn.com/_Secure/0LQAAALkPIVwlwazBaBtFwEYJbSyWPbdod2d4YJMkjvpnn3r8Abn4Hb*CWl2mlrKaysDlJTcgeTs/PoZ1.jpg"><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--><br>
I start by pulling the 3 Giants around the front of the building (1,2,3).  These are easy to split by conventional FD pulling.  <br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://communities.msn.com/_Secure/0LQAzALoPSVyJ*NZBVAjuY6sBAi3htWb2AIsHsO4HWXMO2HF5W6VYpNr59JEdQH5fROsvJ8BT6!0/PoZ2.jpg"><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--><br>
Then I'll agro the middle PoZ and FD at the shown location...4 with path back more slowly than 5 and 6 because he has to walk around and through the door....so he can easily be singled out by observing when the other two reset.  Stand and let him run at you then FD and let a Chain Puller with a bow snag him off of you.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://communities.msn.com/_Secure/0LQAvQrsPcVwbo*TPNGtUgJ!fx8yqP2id4FadG*UC6cdqM5oLU0mkZ1WZu3RUg6ZTuZzpgZ1JG!U/PoZ3.jpg"><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--><br>
Next agro 5 again by standing directly in front of him then running straight back....6 will hit the wall before he comes through the door so when you FD he'll be a few steps behind 5.  Stand when you see 6 reset and Chain Pull 5.  <br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://communities.msn.com/_Secure/0OABFVAASt!yN816!3E4AwC2xjU**HJswXZCk8yXHrstuVChsq5i2hpLxDDC*luHppUDkGGoru3eztfSabLrvABnWF*doRG05/PoZ4(1).jpg"><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--><br>
Then you're free to piss off and pull 6 however you wish! <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->      <br>
<br>
Bjorak the Cold will be down a ramp on the sharp right once inside the door.  He'll have to be split from a Gladiator to be single pulled.  This is easily done, though...just pull them both up and one or the other will normally path back alone after you FD.<br>
<br>
Hope this helps!<br>
<br>
