This is the best way to get SoM if you're on Giant faction or only have 1 or 2 groups available and taking Prots isn't an option.  <br>
<br>
It's very easy to get Bjrack solo, all you need to do is run up and attack the gladiator, melee him for about 8-10 seconds.  At this time you will see Bjrackor run toward the wall away from the arena.  After about 8-10 seconds of meleeing the gladiator, run out to the spot marked x. (Once you run towards the door, the gladiator will also take off the same direction that Bjrack did, so don't worry about him following you)  Bjrack should warp to you at that point, FD as soon as he hits you and then have your Tank tag and the rest is gravy.  <br>
<br>
